subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution: Red Sea, Mombasa , Gulf of Mannar, Gulf of Tonkin , Okinawa , Japan , Philippines and Indonesia to Hawaii and the Society Islands (Hayashi, 1975; Chace, 1997 ;
Prakash et al ., 2016
). Presently, it is found that the distribution of the species is extended to Lakshadweep Islands.
